# Thread Viewer Overhaul

## Context
The thread viewer needs a massive visual and functional overhaul to include user profiles overlays, dynamic side tiles, table of contents parsing, role-based background colors, and an embedded video player.

## Goal
- Completely revamp the `view-thread` route with a rich tile-based grid system.
- Support infinite-loading viewers and likers.
- Add dynamic role colors to thread backgrounds.

## Non-Goals
- We are not changing the core thread creation or editing flows.

## Steps
1. Execute DB Migration & Backend for Roles Color.
2. Implement Profile Hover Overlay & Header Update.
3. Build Grid Layout & Table of Contents parser.
4. Implement Infinite Tiles for Views & Likes.
5. Migrate YouTube Player into a dedicated thread tile.

## Verification
- Backend tests pass for roles and thread endpoints.
- Frontend builds cleanly and tiles are responsive on mobile.

